```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant MainApp as SmartAgent3 Main App (Node.js)
    participant LLM
    participant DB as Database (MySQL/TiDB)
    participant Emotions as Emotions-Express (Python)

    User->>+Frontend: 1. Sends message
    Frontend->>+MainApp: 2. Forwards message (tRPC/WebSocket)

    MainApp->>+DB: 3. Retrieves conversation history & user profile
    DB-->>-MainApp: Returns data

    MainApp->>MainApp: 4. Calls Memory System to search relevant memories
    MainApp->>DB: Searches memories
    DB-->>MainApp: Returns memories

    MainApp->>MainApp: 5. Calls Personality Engine to build System Prompt (with memories, profile, persona)

    MainApp->>+LLM: 6. Supervisor: Classify & Plan (using dynamic prompt)
    LLM-->>-MainApp: Returns plan/next step

    MainApp->>MainApp: 7. Supervisor: Execute step via Domain Agent (e.g., call MCP tool)

    MainApp->>+LLM: 8. Supervisor: Generate final text response (with emotion tag instructions)
    LLM-->>-MainApp: Returns text with [emotion:happy] tags

    MainApp->>+Emotions: 9. Sends text for emotional rendering
    Emotions->>Emotions: Parses tags, generates TTS audio & actions
    Emotions-->>-MainApp: 10. Streams back multimodal data (text, audio, actions)

    MainApp-->>-Frontend: 11. Streams multimodal response
    Frontend-->>-User: 12. Renders text, plays audio, shows avatar animation

    par Asynchronous Operations
        MainApp->>MainApp: 13. (async) Memory Extraction
        MainApp->>+LLM: Extracts new memories from conversation
        LLM-->>-MainApp: Returns structured memories
        MainApp->>+DB: Saves new memories
        DB-->>-MainApp: 
    end
```
